{"comments":"Bounded Index Types for GPU Wire Format.\n\n## Purpose\n\nAt billion-agent scale, we need two identity systems:\n\n1. **UUID5** (global): Deterministic identity for attestation, caching,\n   deduplication. Same inputs → same UUID5 across all agents.\n\n2. **Indices** (local): Efficient wire-format identifiers for GPU dispatch.\n   u32 fits in registers, enables batching, minimizes bandwidth.\n\n## The Registry Pattern\n\n```\nUUID5 (global identity) ←→ Registry ←→ Index (local dispatch)\n```\n\nThe runtime maintains registries mapping UUID5s to indices:\n- FontRegistry: UUID5 of font definition → FontId\n- GlyphRegistry: UUID5 of glyph path data → GlyphId\n- PathDataRegistry: UUID5 of path commands → PathDataId\n\n## Bounded by Construction\n\nEach index type has explicit bounds for its domain:\n- GlyphId: u32 (0 to 4,294,967,295) — enough for all Unicode + variants\n- FontId: u32 (0 to 4,294,967,295) — supports billion AI-generated brands\n- PathDataId: u32 (0 to 4,294,967,295) — deduplicated path instances\n\n## Wire Format\n\nAll indices serialize as little-endian u32 (4 bytes) in the binary format.\nThis matches WebGPU/Vulkan conventions and GPU register sizes.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"GlyphId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[107,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[107,1]},"title":"eqGlyphId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"GlyphId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[108,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[108,1]},"title":"ordGlyphId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"GlyphId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,49],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"showGlyphId"}],"comments":"Index into glyph path data registry.\n\nBounded to u32 (0 to 2^32-1). At billion-agent scale with AI-generated\nfonts, we need room for:\n- Unicode: ~150,000 codepoints\n- Variants: ligatures, alternates, stylistic sets\n- AI-generated: novel glyphs for brand differentiation\n\nu32 provides ~4 billion slots — sufficient for foreseeable scale.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[105,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[105,1]},"title":"GlyphId"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"FontId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[138,1]},"title":"eqFontId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"FontId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[139,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[139,1]},"title":"ordFontId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"FontId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[142,47],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[141,1]},"title":"showFontId"}],"comments":"Index into font registry.\n\nAt billion-agent scale, each AI company may generate unique fonts for\nbrand differentiation. u32 supports ~4 billion distinct fonts.\n\nNote: Upgraded from u16 (65K limit) to u32 for billion-agent scale.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[136,1]},"title":"FontId"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"PathDataId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[168,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[168,1]},"title":"eqPathDataId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"PathDataId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[169,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[169,1]},"title":"ordPathDataId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Index"],"PathDataId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[172,55],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Index.purs","start":[171,1]},"title":"showPathDataId"}],"comments":"Index into share